--- !u!114 &967305426
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 967305424}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 7bd36737155f37a48a7d45e5db553f61, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  slides:
  - image: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 27716805a86762342bdafdbac2a31d1b, type: 3}
    caption: Welcome, Soldier. You are stranded. Your primary goal is to get to the
      safehouse and keep the signal beacon powered until extraction in 6 hours. Use
      WASD to move and the Mouse to look around.
  - image: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 562a50b853e49784884c536066620698, type: 3}
    caption: "The safehouse is high up, and you can\u2019t reach the generator! Use
      the Scroll Wheel to choose the best object to help you reach it. You can see
      the object details on the right side of the screen."
  - image: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 8ff63e723e53dcf4ab7f2ea613651a09, type: 3}
    caption: Middle-Click the scroll button to enter placement mode and see a preview.
      Left-Click to place the object. You can use materials to build objects to help
      you move around and fortify your place. The amount of material needed for each
      object is based on  its health and ratio of materials.
  - image: {fileID: 21300000, guid: edf684b707d67f643a02eedbd7a095a8, type: 3}
    caption: 'The beacon consumes energy constantly. Approach the generator and Right-Click
      to enter the game. '
  - image: {fileID: 21300000, guid: c8d7696cb5197b24daf78122afae2a79, type: 3}
    caption: Click on 2 cards to see if the fractions and decimals match. Each check
      uses 1 Ore. Each correct match increases the signal's energy.
  - image: {fileID: 21300000, guid: c78d700113846e64f995c24b6d5a7da9, type: 3}
    caption: Low on building materials and ores? Mine in the nearby forest to resupply.
  - image: {fileID: 21300000, guid: d5d548792906a2c4886c7d4b707c85d3, type: 3}
    caption: Enemies are tracking you! They can hurt you and damage your objects.
      Each of them has equations and options across their build. Shoot the correct
      answer using a Left-Click!
  - image: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 9fa613473c95d0545abcabef993a1293, type: 3}
    caption: Running low on ammo? Search for ammo crates nearby and Right-Click to
      enter the game to unlock it.
  - image: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 7ce66c8876c06bc4a9f4d4e62c80e4fc, type: 3}
    caption: Identify the number pattern and enter the missing value to unlock the
      box. You can exit this ammo box and come if you need to think it over. Once
      you click submit the box will be used.
  slideA: {fileID: 550738965}
  slideB: {fileID: 1624180517}
  imageA: {fileID: 915209534}
  captionA: {fileID: 951939366}
  groupA: {fileID: 550738962}
  imageB: {fileID: 25343513}
  captionB: {fileID: 1566207164}
  groupB: {fileID: 1624180514}
  duration: 0.25
  slideDistance: 900
